Company Overview of Putnam Variable Trust - Putnam VT Small Cap Value Fund



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Putnam Variable Trust - Putnam VT Small Cap Value Fund is an open-ended variable annuity equity mutual fund launched and managed by Putnam Investment Management, LLC. The fund is co-managed by Putnam Investments Limited. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in the value stocks of small-cap companies. The fund focuses on factors such as company’s valuation, financial strength, growth potential, and competitive position in its industry, projected future earnings, cash flows, and dividends to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against ...
Putnam Variable Trust - Putnam VT Small Cap Value Fund is an open-ended variable annuity equity mutual fund launched and managed by Putnam Investment Management, LLC. The fund is co-managed by Putnam Investments Limited. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The fund invests in the stocks of companies operating across diversified sectors. It primarily invests in the value stocks of small-cap companies. The fund focuses on factors such as company’s valuation, financial strength, growth potential, and competitive position in its industry, projected future earnings, cash flows, and dividends to create its portfolio. It benchmarks the performance of its portfolio against the Russell 2000 Value Index. Putnam Variable Trust- Putnam VT Small Cap Value Fund was formed on April 30, 1999 and is domiciled in the United States.
